Text: pspxxx delivers once again! Thanks so much for taking the time and effort.

Well Time Team Lovers...Today is Sunday...its not a good one cause its the last program of the series 20...and the last Episode of Time Team...ever(?)..Ok a couple of specials planned for 2014..not the same... Minority TV suffers again. Now its the chance of National Geographic/Discovery to steal it away from C4...

Thanks so much with these episodes. Especially since you didn't get caught up in the Episode 5 - 'Warriors' shenanigans!

As someone with no avenue to this show, I really appreciate the time and effort and generosity shown by you and seeders.

On to the Specials!!
Tim Taylor, Time Team's producer, is developing the concept for a show called Dig Village. They have a YouTube channel.
